summary:
10+ years of experience in marketing and communications with international experience in various sectors including impact investing, crowdfunding, education, health and wellness, and more. 

I consider myself curious, people-centric and passionate about developing engaging content. I enjoy connecting people and building communities to support great concepts and initiatives. 

I believe in making an impact through purpose-driven branding and marketing for companies around the globe. An expert in working remotely, efficiently juggling several projects at once and inspired by deadlines.
